data.meta_desc: PROOF THAT a basketball is flat I used the zetetic method to examine whether a basketball is really a ball or is it actually flat. Upon taking a closer look with a macro lens on my Nikon P900 I can only conclude that the surface of a basketball while bumpy does not appear to have any curvature. Therefore basketballs are flat. Their roundness must be some kind of illusion caused by perspective and mirages. Flat Earth Society,Troll.  Memes.
